04:07.107 --> 04:09.525
How the hell can you
not love Thanksgiving?

04:09.527 --> 04:11.427
Six hours of cooking,
ten minutes of eating

04:11.429 --> 04:12.795
and then a food coma?

04:12.797 --> 04:14.097
What's wrong with a food coma?
Give me

04:14.099 --> 04:15.415
any other holiday, please.

04:15.417 --> 04:17.500
Detectives.
What do you got, Sarge?

04:17.502 --> 04:19.619
Hispanic male,
stabbed to death,

04:19.620 --> 04:21.204
found by the owner
of this bar over there.

04:21.206 --> 04:22.989
Yeah, I came out to
take out some empties,

04:22.991 --> 04:24.507
and I almost stepped on him.

04:24.509 --> 04:25.675
You ever seen him before?

04:25.677 --> 04:27.794
Just inside,
watching the football.

04:27.796 --> 04:29.429
I'm missing
a football game tonight?

04:29.431 --> 04:32.432
I think he means soccer.
Yeah, Venezuela versus Chile!

04:32.434 --> 04:33.716
Right!

04:33.718 --> 04:35.601
Soccer's not football.

04:35.603 --> 04:40.506
And it looks like the game
is officially over for this guy.

04:40.508 --> 04:42.775
Wallet...

04:42.777 --> 04:45.812
appears to be intact.

04:45.814 --> 04:47.730
Wasn't a robbery.

04:47.732 --> 04:50.400
Single stab wound
to the chest.

04:50.402 --> 04:51.818
Judging by
the angle,

04:51.820 --> 04:54.070
the killer is left-handed.

04:54.072 --> 04:57.640
Gabriel Vega, 26 years old.

04:57.642 --> 04:59.492
He lives about three blocks
from here.

04:59.494 --> 05:01.828
I'd say Mr. Vega came
out for a smoke,

05:01.830 --> 05:03.379
killer approached
to bum one,

05:03.381 --> 05:05.298
stabbed him before he lit up.

05:05.300 --> 05:08.051
You psychic?
'Cause I only see the one.

05:08.053 --> 05:10.036
Uh, no. There's another one
right there.

05:10.038 --> 05:11.754
Saw it on
the way in.

05:11.756 --> 05:13.256
You got

05:13.258 --> 05:14.490
security cameras
here?

05:14.492 --> 05:17.827
No, I don't but other businesses
in the area do.

05:17.829 --> 05:19.429
All right. Uh, Sarge,

05:19.431 --> 05:22.381
can you have your guys round 'em
all up, everything within

05:22.383 --> 05:24.517
a five-block radius?
Of course.

05:24.519 --> 05:25.719
Well, if this isn't a robbery,

05:25.720 --> 05:28.237
you got a motive for why
somebody wanted him dead?

05:30.025 --> 05:33.242
Maybe he was cheering
for the wrong soccer team.

05:37.948 --> 05:39.866
Step aside. Kill those TVs.

05:39.868 --> 05:41.984
Please, sir, this is one of my
biggest nights of the year.

05:41.986 --> 05:43.536
Not anymore it isn't.
<i>Por favor...</i>

05:43.538 --> 05:45.588
Terry Giondo here

05:45.590 --> 05:47.807
for Master Blend 3000.

05:47.809 --> 05:49.709
Hey! A minute left in the half!

05:49.711 --> 05:51.044
Shut up!
And we're kicking

05:51.046 --> 05:52.078
their asses!

05:52.080 --> 05:53.212
Shut up!

05:53.214 --> 05:54.847
Now, here's how
it's gonna go down.

05:54.849 --> 05:57.517
I want Chile fans
over there on the bench,

05:57.519 --> 05:59.919
Venezuela fans over here
on the bar.

05:59.921 --> 06:02.772
Move your asses.
Let's go. Let's go!

